<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-6667] Mean cells per sstable is calculated incorrectly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6667</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We currently take the average of the mean for each partition, rather than correctly weighting by cell count.  This affects hint paging as well as index selectivity calculation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12693615">CASSANDRA-6667</key>
